title: Pomme De Terre Food Co-op
description: Pomme De Terre is a volunteer-run community based co-op. They offer a variety of vegan staples (tofu, tempeh, nutritional yeast, kombucha and more). The board of directors is working to expand their fresh produce selection, complimenting their bulk goods, frozen foods, supplements and snacks. Volunteers get up to 20% off their groceries. Members and seniors get a 5% discount.
